  "narrative": "# Turn 74\n\n*7 commanders issued orders this turn.*\n\n## Strategic Decisions\n\n### CURATOR (artifact collector)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W25, W25, W19, W30.\n\n### NOMAD (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W30, W25, W16.\n\n### PROPHET (apostle)\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 2 fleets; unloaded at 1 destinations; commissioned 12 new ships.\n\n### REAVER (pirate)\n\nDispatched 4 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W9, W15, W22, W28.\n\nEconomic activity: loaded cargo onto 3 fleets; commissioned 13 new ships.\n\n### SOLARIS (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W12, W6.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 2 units of industry.\n\n### TERRAN (empire builder)\n\nDispatched 2 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W16, W19.\n\nEconomic activity: invested in 2 units of industry.\n\n### TRADER (merchant)\n\nDispatched 3 fleets across the galaxy \u2014 targeting worlds W19, W27, W19.\n\nEconomic activity: commissioned 6 new ships.\n\n## Consequences\n\n### Territorial Shifts\n\n- **SOLARIS** seized control of W6 (previously REAVER).\n\n- **NOMAD** seized control of W30 (previously TRADER).\n\n### Fleet Movements\n\n- **CURATOR** moved: F7\u2192W25, F8\u2192W25\n\n- **NOMAD** moved: F15\u2192W30, F16\u2192W16\n\n- **REAVER** repositioned 4 fleets across the sector.\n\n- **SOLARIS** moved: F2\u2192W12, F1\u2192W6\n\n- **TERRAN** moved: F13\u2192W16, F14\u2192W19\n\n- **TRADER** moved: F3\u2192W19, F4\u2192W27\n\n### Production\n\n- **PROPHET** launched 0 new ships.\n\n- **REAVER** launched 0 new ships.\n\n- **TRADER** launched 6 new ships.\n\n- **SOLARIS** built 2 industry.\n\n- **TERRAN** built 2 industry.\n\n### Diplomacy\n\n- **TRADER** sent a message to **NOMAD**: *\"Alliance Proposal from TRADER\"*\n"
